abilities.name: Living Bombs
abilities.description: This unit automatically passes Morale tests. abilities.name: Floating Death (Mucolid Spore)
abilities.description: A Mucolid Spore explodes if it is within 3" of any enemy units at the end of any Charge phase. The Mucolid Spore is then destroyed.
